---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Projects"
  description="Mechanical engineering projects by Jacky Huynh."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Projects</p>

    <h1>Engineering Projects</h1>

    <p class="intro">
      A selection of engineering projects focused on design, simulation,
      prototyping, and problem-solving.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="project-grid">
    <a class="project-card" href="/projects/propeller-optimization">
      <img
        src="/images/projects/boat-propeller.jpg"
        alt="Autonomous Boat Propeller Optimization"
      />

      <div class="project-content">
        <h2>Autonomous Boat Propeller Optimization</h2>

        <p>
          Designed, simulated, and tested propeller geometries to improve
          performance for an autonomous boat platform.
        </p>

        <span>CAD • Simulation • Testing</span>

        <span class="card-link">
          View Project →
        </span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a class="project-card" href="/projects/boat-propulsion">
      <img
        src="/images/projects/boat-propulsion.jpg"
        alt="Boat Propulsion System Design"
      />

      <div class="project-content">
        <h2>Boat Propulsion System Design</h2>

        <p>
          Selected and integrated motors, batteries, shafts, and supporting
          components to optimize performance while meeting project constraints.
        </p>

        <span>System Design • Analysis • Component Selection</span>

        <span class="card-link">
          View Project →
        </span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a class="project-card" href="/projects/lidar-casing">
      <img
        src="/images/projects/lidar-casing.jpg"
        alt="Water-Resistant LiDAR Camera Casing"
      />

      <div class="project-content">
        <h2>Water-Resistant LiDAR Camera Casing</h2>

        <p>
          Designed and fabricated a protective enclosure for a LiDAR camera
          system used in outdoor environments.
        </p>

        <span>Design • Prototyping • Manufacturing</span>

        <span class="card-link">
          View Project →
        </span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a class="project-card" href="/projects/c-clamp-analysis">
      <img
        src="/images/projects/c-clamp.jpg"
        alt="C-Clamp CAD Model and Failure Analysis"
      />

      <div class="project-content">
        <h2>C-Clamp CAD Model and Failure Analysis</h2>

        <p>
          Reconstructed a 1:1 CAD model of a C-clamp and performed finite
          element analysis to identify structural weaknesses and failure points.
        </p>

        <span>SOLIDWORKS • FEA • Simulation</span>

        <span class="card-link">
          View Project →
        </span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a class="project-card" href="/projects/mini-forklift">
      <img
        src="/images/projects/mini-forklift.jpg"
        alt="Mini Forklift Design and Assembly"
      />

      <div class="project-content">
        <h2>Mini Forklift Design and Assembly</h2>

        <p>
          Designed and assembled a functional mini forklift while validating
          performance through torque, gear, and load calculations.
        </p>

        <span>MATLAB • Mechanical Design • System Integration</span>

        <span class="card-link">
          View Project →
        </span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a class="project-card" href="/projects/senior-design">
      <img
        src="/images/projects/senior-design.jpg"
        alt="Senior Design Project"
      />

      <div class="project-content">
        <h2>Senior Design Project</h2>

        <p>
          Led a multidisciplinary team through the design, planning, and
          execution of a capstone engineering project.
        </p>

        <span>Leadership • Project Management • Systems Integration</span>

        <span class="card-link">
          View Project →
        </span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .intro {
    max-width: 42rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .project-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .project-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 320px 1fr;
    gap: 0;

    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 24px;

    overflow: hidden;

    transition:
      transform 0.2s ease,
      box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .project-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .project-card img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 260px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;

    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .project-card:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  .project-content {
    padding: 1.5rem;

    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .project-content h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .project-content p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .project-content span:not(.card-link) {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.4;
    opacity: 0.8;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .card-link {
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;

    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;

    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .project-card:hover .card-link {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .project-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .project-card img {
      height: 220px;
    }

    .project-content {
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>